Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 15:29:10 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: redesign exit popup UI - premium brand treatment

- Gradient header band with animated shine sweep
- Hero cart-value anchor (34px) for loss-aversion impact
- Eyebrow micro-label, tighter copy
- Gift badge + discount pill restyled with gradients
- CTA lift-on-hover, deeper shadow
- Trust footer: '100% Authentic, imported from USA'
- Poppins font (matches storefront)
- 24px corners, spring easing
- a11y: role=dialog, aria-modal, focus-visible, reduced-motion
